{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "trrcms-buildings-v1",
		"name": "TRRCMS — 02. Buildings & Assignments",
		"description": "# TRRCMS — Buildings & Assignments\n\nBuilding CRUD, polygon/radius search, property units, and building assignment workflow (UC-012).\n\n**Audience:** Admin, Data Manager, Desktop Team\n\n**Requires:** `accessToken` from 01_Auth collection\n\n**Environment:** `TRRCMS_Development.postman_environment.json`\n\n## Enum Reference\n\n### PropertyUnitType\n| Value | Name | Arabic |\n|-------|------|--------|\n| 1 | Apartment | شقة سكنية |\n| 2 | Shop | محل تجاري |\n| 3 | Office | مكتب |\n| 4 | Warehouse | مستودع |\n| 5 | Other | أخرى |\n\n### PropertyUnitStatus\n| Value | Name | Arabic |\n|-------|------|--------|\n| 1 | Occupied | مشغول |\n| 2 | Vacant | شاغر |\n| 3 | Damaged | متضرر |\n| 4 | UnderRenovation | قيد الترميم |\n| 5 | Uninhabitable | غير صالح للسكن |\n| 6 | Locked | مغلق |\n| 99 | Unknown | غير معروف |\n\n### TransferStatus (حالة النقل)\n| Value | Name | Arabic |\n|-------|------|--------|\n| 1 | Pending | قيد الانتظار |\n| 2 | InProgress | جاري النقل |\n| 3 | Transferred | تم النقل |\n| 4 | Failed | فشل النقل |\n| 5 | Cancelled | ملغي |\n| 6 | PartialTransfer | نقل جزئي |\n| 7 | Synchronized | متزامن |\n\n### Priority (الأولوية)\n| Value | Name | Arabic |\n|-------|------|--------|\n| Normal | عادي |\n| High | عالي |\n| Urgent | عاجل |",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{accessToken}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"item": [
