			"description": "## 📋 Building Assignments (UC-012)\n\n**Requires:** Administrator or DataManager role\n\n**Permissions:**\n- Buildings_View (4000) - Search buildings, view assignments\n- Buildings_Assign (4003) - Create/cancel assignments\n\n**Workflow:**\n1. Search buildings (by hierarchy, radius, or polygon)\n2. Select property units for revisit (optional)\n3. Get available field collectors\n4. Assign buildings to collector\n5. Monitor assignment status\n\n**TransferStatus Flow:**\n```\nPending (1) → InProgress (2) → Transferred (3) → Synchronized (7)\n                              ↓\n                           Failed (4) → Retry\n                              ↓\n                        Cancelled (5)\n```\n\n**Priority Values:** Normal, High, Urgent"
